<p>Pump.fun is built for adults with capital to risk. In practice, reporting and lawsuits have raised concerns that <strong>young people</strong> can access trading and streams without meaningful age verification. A <strong>2025 lawsuit</strong> (reported in the press) alleged the platform marketed to minors without adequate safeguards. Even when someone is legally an adult, impulsive trading and social pressure can still cause serious harm.</p>

