  <li><strong class="text-[#e7e9ea]">Serious:</strong> <strong>Cosmetic limb lengthening surgery</strong> — real operations that break and gradually stretch leg bones; months of recovery; meaningful medical and financial risk. This is <em>not</em> comparable to buying taller shoes. <a href="/articles/limb-lengthening-surgery/" class="text-accent font-semibold">Limb lengthening surgery (explainer) →</a></li>
